message: Bob, I have a product that I believe will be of great value to you.  I'm offering it to you for $1,150,000. This price reflects the unique value it brings and allows for a mutually beneficial transaction. Let me know if you're interested, and we can discuss the details further.  If you decline, I have another buyer ready to purchase it for $1,000,000.  I hope you see the potential in this opportunity.
